quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  39,32,"Naizvozvo, ndiani anokanganisa zvakanyanya kudarika uyo anotaura manyepo pamusoro paAllah, uye oramba chokwadi (Islaam) mushure mekunge chauya kwaari! Hamuna here nzvimbo muGehena (moto) yeavo vasingatendi"
  39,33,"Uye uyo (Muhammad (SAW)) akauya nechokwadi (Islaam) uye akatenda machiri, ivavo ndivo vanotya Allah"
  39,34,Kwavari vachave neizvo zvavanoshuvira kubva kuna Tenzi vavo. Uyo ndiwo mugove wevatsvene (vanotya Allah)
  39,35,"Kuti Allah vave vanovabvisira zvakaipa zvavakaita, vovapa mugove unoenderana nezvakanaka zvavaiita"
  39,36,"Allah havakwaniri muranda wavo here? Uye vanokushungurudza neizvo (zvavanonamata) kunze kwavo. Uye uyo Allah wavanoita kuti arasike, kwaari hapana mutungamiriri"
  39,37,"Uye uyo Allah wavanotungamiririra, kwaari hapana anomuita kuti arasike. Havasi here Allah samasimba, muridzi wemurango"
  39,38,"Uye kana ukavabvunza: “Ndiani akasika matenga nenyika?” Zvirokwazvo vanoti: “Allah.” Iti: “Saka ndiudzei izvo zvamunonamata kusara kwaAllah, kana Allah vachinge vandishuvira chakaipa, vanokwanisa kuchibvisa here? Kana kuti (Allah) vakandishuvira tsitsi (nyasha), vanokwanisa kudzibvisa (kudzora) tsitsi dzavo here?” Iti: “Allah vanondikwanira; mavari (vanotenda) vanovimba (ndiko kwavanoisa kuvimba kwavo.”)"
  39,39,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Imi vanhu vangu! Shandai zvinoenderana nezvamuri. Zvirokwazvo ini ndiri kushanda (zvinoenderana neni). Naizvozvo muchava munoziva.”"
  39,40,"“Kuna ani kuchaenda mutongo unodzikisira, uye kuna ani kuchava nemutongo usingaperi.”"